      "para_id": "Q001494.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , who built Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , built and restored his spectacular Kasura gate , which brings abundance . ( This ) is part of the door ."
    }
  ],
